<li>February 10<sup>th</sup> 2014 &ndash; &nbsp;Reviews decisions</li>
<li>February 17<sup>th</sup> 2014 &ndash; Camera Ready Copy of abstracts due (via EasyChair), register for event (fee &pound;135, includes evening meal 6th March, link to follow)</li>
<li>5<sup>th</sup> March 2014 &ndash; John Cook&rsquo;s Professorial Lecture, all attending Symposium are invited, as are those not involved in the Symposium: <a href="http://info.uwe.ac.uk/events/event.aspx?id=14630" target="_blank">Social Network Innovation in the Internet's Global Coffeehouses: Pandora, Learning Layers, Design Seeking and Scaling</a>.</li>
<li>6<sup>th</sup> - 7<sup>th</sup> March 2014 &ndash; Symposium takes place, Watershed, Bristol UK</li>
