              <title>Team up - Using OER to create curriculum for mobile era</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/7394</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/7394</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>Goal :</p>
<p>Help educators using OER to create learning materials for mobile era by developing a solution or an eCourse</p>
<p>Dream:</p>
<p>OER + Learning Design + Self-publishing from educators + Mobile learning + Game elements (storytelling, playfulness)</p>
<p>Experts in different areas speak their own languages, &nbsp;but best solutions often appear at the overlap of many areas. Have you thought of the best answer from an expert's view and a non-expert's view ? umm, in a dream? Maybe you don't want to join this team idea, but you are very welcome to throw in here any example or idea that comes into your mind. No limit.</p>
<p>Interested in heterogeneous network, welcome in.</p>
