              <description><![CDATA[<p>Warwick Medical School has produced an app, '<a title="http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/newsandevents/pressreleases/anatomy_app" href="http://www2.warwick.ac.uk/newsandevents/pressreleases/anatomy_app">Aspects  of Anatomy</a>', comprising 38 short teaching videos using real, plastinated  prosections of the lungs, thorax and the arm, from shoulder to  hand:</p>
